org.genericsystem.api.core

Interface Generic

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Generic>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Attribute, Engine, Holder, Link, Node, Relation, Tree, Type

    public interface Generic
extends java.lang.Comparable<Generic>
    Generic is main interface of each node of the internal graph.
    Author:
    Nicolas Feybesse, Michael Ory
